WEBVTT

00:03:59.560 --> 00:04:02.240
that feeds the ocean ecosystem.

00:04:03.120 --> 00:04:05.696
How does this tiny amount of biomass

00:04:05.720 --> 00:04:07.776
produce as much as all the plants on land?

00:04:07.800 --> 00:04:10.336
Well, they don't have trunks and stems

00:04:10.360 --> 00:04:13.296
and flowers and fruits
and all that to maintain.

00:04:13.320 --> 00:04:16.136
All they have to do is grow and divide
and grow and divide.

00:04:16.160 --> 00:04:19.760
They're really lean
little photosynthesis machines.

00:04:21.519 --> 00:04:22.720
They really crank.

00:04:27.400 --> 00:04:31.296
So there are thousands
